Geographic coordinate conversion

this plugin convert input coordinate value to decimal degree

All of the following are supported ways to write geographic coordinates:
 *   40:26:46N,79:56:55W
 *   40:26:46.302N 79:56:55.903W
 *   40°26′47″N 79°58′36″W
 *   40d 26′ 47″ N 79d 58′ 36″ W
 *   40.446195N 79.948862W
 *   40.446195, -79.948862
 *   40° 26.7717, -79° 56.93172
 
 http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geographic_coordinate_conversion
 
 usage: 
 
```html
<fieldset class="coords">
	<input class="latitude" type="text"  /> <- latitude<br />
	<input class="longitude" type="text" /> <- longitude<br />						
</fieldset>

<script type="text/javascript" >
	$(function(){				
		$('.coords').geoConvertCoords();
	});
</script>
```